---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Lab | Creative Portfolio">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Interactive Lab</p>
    <h1>Lab</h1>
    <p>
      这里之后放你的鼠标动效、流体光效、AI 辅助网页、Canvas / WebGL 实验。
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="lab-grid">
    <article class="lab-card">
      <span>Experiment 01</span>
      <h2>Fluid Cursor</h2>
      <p>鼠标流体、粒子拖尾、光晕和惯性控制。</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lab-card">
      <span>Experiment 02</span>
      <h2>AI-assisted Web</h2>
      <p>使用 AI 编程工具辅助制作的网页交互实验。</p>
    </article>

    <article class="lab-card">
      <span>Experiment 03</span>
      <h2>Visual Playground</h2>
      <p>图像、文字、动画和网页视觉系统实验。</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>